{"tid":2029613,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港美國商會促當局釐清香港國安法定義及內容","createTime":"2020-05-22T10:13:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-23T00:27:18.000Z","uid":21470,"like":178,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":98,"replies":[{"pid":"e559be7a420777978403a4a87b55e48ed5bdc73b","tid":2029613,"uid":21470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:13:54.000Z","msg":"香港美國商會促當局釐清香港國安法定義及內容<br />\n22.05.2020 18:06<br />\n<br />\n香港美國商會發表聲明，認為人大審議香港國安法的草案，是繞過香港立法程序，將損害香港國際金融的前景，要求當局必須釐清國安的定義，以及條例的詳細內容等，以釋除商界憂慮。美商會指，香港和內地的分別在於自由、獨立司法制度及結集自由等，這些要素一直推動香港繁榮，令本港成為全球頂尖的國際商業中心。商會關注國安法如何影響香港法治，包括會否限制網絡、新聞和個人自由，亦憂慮在港外國人在法例下會否受威脅。<br />\n<br />\n美商會認為，香港已經陷入中美貿易磨擦之中，擔心國安法日後會成為中美磨擦的「避雷針」，強調若果香港貿易和資訊自由等被削弱，將無人成為贏家。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289451&amp;csid=261_341\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.881903.com%2FPage%2FZH-TW%2Fnewsdetail.aspx%3FItemId%3D1289451%26csid%3D261_341&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=63c515d6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.881903.com/Page/ZH-TW/newsdetail.aspx?ItemId=1289451&amp;csid=261_341</a>"},{"pid":"19294b418ce7caf7c244eee85ccb1b1bf252149f","tid":2029613,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:14:55.000Z","msg":"Press Release : AmCham calls for clarification of Beijing&rsquo;s National Security Law for HK<br />\nMay 22, 2020<br />\n<br />\nAmCham calls for clarification of Beijing&rsquo;s National Security Law for Hong Kong as risk rises over the city&rsquo;s future business prospects<br />\n<br />\nMay 22, 2020 &ndash; HONG KONG &ndash; The freedoms that distinguish Hong Kong from the mainland, such as an independent judiciary and freedom of assembly, have long helped the city prosper as one of the world&rsquo;s top international business centers.<br />\n<br />\nAn NPC announcement that it will bypass the Hong Kong legislative process to enact a Hong Kong security law may jeopardize future prospects for international business, particularly if a long list of details is not spelled out and clarified.<br />\n<br />\nAlso alarmingly for US business, national security legislation as proposed could lead to a tit-for-tat between Washington and Beijing that eventually curtails Hong Kong&rsquo;s special treatment as defined in the Hong Kong Policy Act. The city is already caught in the crossfire of a growing US-China trade war, and the proposed national security legislation could be a lightning rod for further friction.<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Hong Kong today stands as a model of free trade, strong governance, free flow of information and efficiency,&rdquo; said Robert Grieves, AmCham Chairman. &ldquo;No one wins if the foundation for Hong Kong&rsquo;s role as a prime international business and financial center is eroded.&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;Definition and details are really necessary to alleviate a fear factor developing in the business community. A Beijing inspired national security law leaves open an interpretation of how such an act will be enforced. How will it affect the rule of law? Will it mean limiting online, press and personal freedoms? People may also ask whether Beijing&rsquo;s concern over foreign interference adds an element of risk to foreigners living here,&rdquo; said Tara Joseph, AmCham President.<br />\n<br />\nFinally the enactment of a vaguely defined national security law will make it harder to recruit and retain top tier talent. Already recruitment of international talent to Hong Kong has slowed. The Hong Kong Government could help by stepping in to ensure the safety of overseas executives, and reassuring international businesses facing new uncertainties here.<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.amcham.org.hk/news/2020-national-security-law\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.amcham.org.hk%2Fnews%2F2020-national-security-law&d=SoQ3z30fPgPyNEU4M2c%2BStjU%2BfyVHSoZbIE78%2FWZKkA%3D&h=607ef8e3\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.amcham.org.hk/news/2020-national-security-law</a>"},{"pid":"e9e564a524ada570ca1e5064b5ad187795c10ed7","tid":2029613,"uid":215876,"like":41,"dislike":1,"score":40,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:15:02.000Z","msg":"賣港總商會想比支那解釋"},{"pid":"a8e3bba4c41872e2990245cf8add1a5957fd77b4","tid":2029613,"uid":15812,"like":17,"dislike":2,"score":15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:15:18.000Z","msg":"受國際認可既中國式攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d2a8288d494b8c07142c3b51f34779e343a43831","tid":2029613,"uid":216683,"like":53,"dislike":0,"score":53,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:15:25.000Z","msg":"驚？<br />\n咁就要撤資啦<br />\n<br />\n撤資？<br />\n有人驚咪會取消國安法<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1691cdced838dced4e31ab2ecfa8f7d3e894198","tid":2029613,"uid":13503,"like":64,"dislike":0,"score":64,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:15:38.000Z","msg":"美國商會當日去澳門都被譴返根本中共唔會俾面你，因為中共知道呢班人有奶就是娘根本無廉恥"},{"pid":"87e0133ccc448ed4baf949e0291c275f799888dd","tid":2029613,"uid":121146,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:15:41.000Z","msg":"釐清左啦  話唔會影響丫嘛  你信嘛？"},{"pid":"9fc4ba9f45ddcece08882ce4e0e924bd93a709d9","tid":2029613,"uid":21470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:15:46.000Z","msg":"新聞稿：美國商會呼籲澄清《香港國家安全法》<br />\n2020年5月22日<br />\n<br />\n美國商會呼籲澄清北京的《香港國家安全法》，因為未來城市商業前景面臨的風險正在增加<br />\n2020年5月22日-香港-獨立的司法機構和集會自由等使香港與大陸區分開來的自由，長期以來一直幫助香港繁榮發展成為世界頂級國際商務中心之一。<br />\n<br />\n全國人大宣布將繞過香港立法程序以頒布香港安全法的公告可能會危害國際業務的未來前景，特別是如果沒有詳細列出並澄清一長串細節。<br />\n<br />\n同樣令美國業務擔憂的是，提議的國家安全立法可能導致華盛頓與北京之間的針鋒相對，最終削弱了《香港政策法》所定義的香港​​特殊待遇。這座城市已經陷入了中美貿易戰不斷發展的交火中，擬議中的國家安全立法可能成為進一步摩擦的避雷針。<br />\n<br />\n美國商會主席羅伯特&middot;格里夫斯（Robert Grieves）表示：&ldquo;今天的香港成為自由貿易，強大治理，信息自由流通和效率的典範。&rdquo; &ldquo;如果削弱香港作為主要國際商業和金融中心的作用的基礎，誰也不會贏。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;定義和細節對於減輕企業界發展的恐懼因素確實是必要的。受北京啟發的《國家安全法》對如何執行這種行為開了一個解釋。它將如何影響法治？這是否意味著限制在線，新聞和個人自由？人們還會問北京對外國干涉的關注是否會給居住在這裡的外國人增加一定的風險，&rdquo;美國商會會長塔拉&middot;約瑟夫（Tara Joseph）說。<br />\n<br />\n最後，模糊定義的國家安全法的頒布將使招募和留住頂級人才變得更加困難。已經開始向香港招募國際人才了。香港政府可以協助確保海外高管的安全，並向在此面臨新不確定性的國際企業放心。<br />\n<br />\nBy Google Translate"},{"pid":"3155f143febf08412e9a7ded137c9f121dae1540","tid":2029613,"uid":41389,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:16:56.000Z","msg":"講咁多做咩呀 撤啦"},{"pid":"4822e106529443d49e2da8c756cb48b3229591a4","tid":2029613,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:17:40.000Z","msg":"知驚？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c1da155ad2490b7add1725cbe590ff5903cff9e9","tid":2029613,"uid":214173,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:17:45.000Z","msg":"隨時用國安法拉幾個外國人黎做人質<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61b504d3dcce7b596f03d57f86bc0c90cb7870c1","tid":2029613,"uid":3801,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:18:02.000Z","msg":"拿 你仆街啦 我記住你 立左法我記去中聯辦舉報你反中亂港"},{"pid":"09c8234893db46952ab19ffa41cbd2f7dcf120f9","tid":2029613,"uid":128417,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:18:07.000Z","msg":"美商會<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ff43396ce9949af6fcaa6f336c2a931ea03b6e9","tid":2029613,"uid":173179,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:18:57.000Z","msg":"宣讀果日就有人過嚟批鬥了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n美國在港間諜機關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e68557fa265199bf4ad75626d3bed612d7a360b","tid":2029613,"uid":13663,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T10:19:24.000Z","msg":"外資開始動搖